核心能力 Competence
■ 職能治療專業知識與理論
具備職能治療專業知識理論基礎，以為專業技能奠基。 Professional Knowledge and Theories of Occupational Therapy
Acuire Professional Knowledge and Theories of Occupational Therapy in order to Develop Therapeutic Skills□ 職能治療專業技能
具備職能治療專業技能，以提供個案職能表現之評估、分析與治療的能力。 Occupational Therapy Therapeutic Skills
Acuire Occupational Therapy Therapeutic Skills to Provide Evaluation, Analysis and Intervention for Clients' Occupational Performance■ 溝通表達及團隊合作之能力
